== Ibikorwa uRwanda ruri gukora mu kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere iva mu binyabiziga na handi hatandukanye. ==
Reta y'uRwanda yashyize imbaraga mu kugabanya bimwe mu bikorwa byangiza ibidukikije cyane ibisohora imyuka yangiza ihumanya ikirere .

